criteria.inclusion_criteria:
1. aged >=18 years;
2. a new focal neurological deficits;
3. met diagnostic criteria of NMOSD;
4. normal liver and kidney function, blood cell, urine  examination;
5. written informed consents were obtained from all subjects.

criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1. abnormal expression or disturbance of consciousness,instable vital signs;
2. diabetes, hyperthyroidism and other endocrine disorders;
3. severe mental illness patients who cannot be cooperated;
4. patients with severe liver or kidney disease and severe systemic chronic wasting disease;
5. gastrointestinal or other bleeding disorder within a mongth;
6. history of myelodysplastic syndrome;
7. use of non steroidal anti-inflammatory drugs;
8. plaque decrease by using injection of heparin or low molecular weight heparin or heparin;
9. history of relative drug allergy;
10. history of important surgeries a week ago;
11. can not cooperate in clinical trial.
